nsform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true;\">如果是大温地区，雇主单位至少应有</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true;\">5</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true;\">名及以上全职员工；大温之外，雇主单位至少应有</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true;\">3</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true;\">名及以上全职员工；</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true; margi